 />"},{"pid":"f7da22df4de54311982be81c78e8fd7a16d8dcf2","tid":381092,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:07:23.000Z","msg":"有 不過佢同我價值觀好大差距。許下一堆堆承諾，但都冇心裝載。可能只係我自己太認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，或者你心裡根本冇我。<br />\n唔知你會唔會睇到呢，中六的鄰桌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba480198c4948e05b19c5a05d9934023b9a8fe3b","tid":381092,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"大把"},{"pid":"e7a250ce6d384fcbfdcc91624c8be5e6f4d7efc8","tid":381092,"uid":102642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"有 但可以點"},{"pid":"8648ab7196cdcc6890d3c127b11409021ba7eeb0","tid":381092,"uid":138670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"有 但佢心目中已經一早將我抹走咗 咩都過去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbad206c236c6aea277a7cf28763e7f302f33f4","tid":381092,"uid":117637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 但佢心目中已經一早將我抹走咗 咩都過去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bf0dcdac09bdb85a3629a0594721ce1764e374","tid":381092,"uid":36740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"有又點冇又點 佢唔會在乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f20cb95a40bfaa668458c6f72525fb50e88612b","tid":381092,"uid":138670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有 但佢心目中已經一早將我抹走咗 咩都過去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好憎我 特登親自走嚟鬧我 仲block曬我所有嘢話以後唔想再見到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bbb9573aad44dc4a14e3c9f9dc3d62d3d8a047","tid":381092,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n但呢個人已經唔存在，因為只有「過去嘅佢」先至好深刻。人係會變 仲可以變好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5ad52d38a4a044fff6dc9e11917a08be8d0aa1","tid":381092,"uid":61679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n但呢個人已經唔存在，因為只有「過去嘅佢」先至好深刻。人係會變 仲可以變好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f4e0df361e8d1287891358368787988a53a201","tid":381092,"uid":23278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:10:32.000Z","msg":"有&hellip;早兩個月走左<br />\n佢走左先知自己幾鐘意佢"},{"pid":"6346e26ed9b78f37a1cf0a4a6b08224e10cd2bdc","tid":381092,"uid":92831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T20:58:58.000Z","msg":"賤得好深刻"},{"pid":"328b4c9d3c2649f503761addd104167133f70872","tid":381092,"uid":8727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T21:01:42.000Z","msg":"原來她有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233d4118f07e36210277ff50ed1319b9512ec47c","tid":381092,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有&hellip;早兩個月走左<br />\n佢走左先知自己幾鐘意佢</blockquote><br />\nrip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a800c7940d28373192775c1c71039ecc9d2e7d1b","tid":381092,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有<br />\n但呢個人已經唔存在，因為只有「過去嘅佢」先至好深刻。人係會變 仲可以變好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smi